node.text:
The 'Comune di Roma Capitale'.
Located in Rome, Italy.
Video by Kirill Neiezhmakov (@neiezhmakov).
.
"It is better to imitate ancient than modern work." — Leonardo da Vinci. #architectureoskar
.
#roma #rome #italy #leonardodavinci

node.text:
Greek golden hour 🔥 #archoskar
The 'Oia' ('Οία').
Located in Oia, Santorini, Greece.
Video by ALEX (@alexpreview).
Song by Sam Smith, 'Fire On Fire'.
.
"The sky broke like an egg into full sunset and the water caught fire." — Pamela Hansford Johnson. #architectureoskar
.
#greek #goldenhour #santorini #oia

node.text:
Contemporary Russian villa ✨ #archoskar
The 'BIANCO' (211 m²).
Designed by Stanislav Ananev, Vorobyeva Tanya & Lidia Ivanova (@ananevdesign, @vorobyeva_tanya_v & @lidiamidia, 2021).
Inspired by the location of Yekaterinburg, Russia.
Visualized by Dmitry Gubarev (@gubarev_dmitry).
 .
"The two most powerful warriors are patience and time." — Leo Tolstoy. #architectureoskar
.
#contemporary #russian #tolstoy #rendering

node.text:
Minimalistic residence 🌴 #archoskar
The 'Caplan House' (250 m²).
Designed by Houses Tulum (@housestulum.mx, 2019).
Located in Tulum, Quintana Roo, Mexico.
Photos by Manolo R Solis (@manolorsolis_fotografia).
.
"Eventually everything connects - people, ideas, objects. The quality of the connections is the key to quality per se." — Charles Eames. #architectureoskar
.
#minimalistic #tulum #mexico #eames

Contemporary brick house ✨ #archoskar
The 'Brick House'.
Designed & visualized by IVAN office (@ivan.architects, 2021).
.
"Architecture starts when you carefully put two bricks together. There it begins." — Ludwig Mies van der Rohe. #architectureoskar
.
#contemporary #brick #rendering #miesvanderrohe

node.text:
Spacious private villa ✨ #archoskar
The 'M3 House' (530 m²).
Designed by OLARQ_Osvaldo Luppi Architects (@olarq_osvaldo_luppi_architects, 2017).
Located in Bendinat, Calvià, Spain.
Photos by Mauricio Fuertes.
Description by OLARQ_Osvaldo Luppi Architects.
.
"Each new situation requires a new architecture." — Jean Nouvel. #architectureoskar
.
In a search for privacy and views to the sea, the starting compact volume is broken up to open up a courtyard. A complex series of transparencies, reflections and long views across the patio strengthens the continuous presence of endless spaces. In a plot inserted in a consolidated residential fabric, with a slight slope in downward direction N-S, a two-story house (plus a basement) has been proposed.
.
#minimalistic #space #private #spain

node.text:
Concrete family home ✨ #archoskar
The 'Kenwood Lee House' (620 m²).
Designed by Cousins & Cousins (@cousinsandcousins).
Located in London, United Kingdom.
Photos by Jack Hobhouse (@jackhobhouse).
Description by Cousins & Cousins.
.
"Recognizing the need is the primary condition for design." — Charles Eames. #architectureoskar
.
'Kenwood Lee House' echoes the traditional vernacular with an uncompromisingly sleek glazing to the rear which affords generous views to the woodlands to the back of the house. A board-marked concrete core forms the top-lit triple height heart to the house, articulating the relationship between intricate material details and the airy, well-considered spaces.
.
#concrete #family #london #unitedkingdom
